{"tid":1907561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家做緊嘢 【黃店同文宣要人】","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T13:58:17.000Z","uid":13866,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"febea3bfc88d72b94afc598876689b9a67d455af","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"有手足見到建制派同啲乜乜同鄉會收老人家資料派口罩 我地緊係要做啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今次18區送暖就唔搞街站派口罩 希望轉個形式嚟個一舉多得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《18區送暖: 一份文宣thx》<br />\n【支持黃色經濟圈 x 推動全民文宣】<br />\n<br />\n活動日期：3月2日(星期一)至3月6日(星期五)<br />\n<br />\n1.  於以下黃店消費，憑收據換領文宣一份，附口罩兩個(每日派發約100份)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n荃灣：台茶小食<br />\n土瓜灣：Six2 Hair Bar Salon<br />\n跑馬地：燒房焗 The Grill Station<br />\n<br />\n2.  屋企缺口罩？自留口罩，將文宣派出去／<br />\n有足夠口罩喇！幫手做文宣，將口罩連同文宣派出去<br />\n<br />\n---&gt; 點樣將份文宣派出去好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n．健談嘅手足可以同街坊嗲兩句，將口罩文宣交到佢地手，可以襯呢個咁好嘅機會提下佢地唔好亂咁填資料換口罩呀<br />\n<br />\n．有手足開發文宣郵差戰線，攞咗份文宣翻去唔係放枱頭嘅，係希望大家唔好淨係喺ig po文宣畀班黃嘅frd睇，一齊將文宣寄出去，寄畀你個藍絲親戚，港豬朋友咩都好，衝出同溫層呀<br />\n<br />\n另外我地都好想做到第二輪嘅【黃店 x 文宣】活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無奈暫時都未搵到下一批嘅口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有黃店/手足有興趣加入/提供口罩嘅可以tg聯絡 @hkpplmobot<br />\n<br />\n18區送暖channel: @hkpplmoo<br />\nFB page: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/30k0ghZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30k0ghZ&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=9cedac07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30k0ghZ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHwp2qL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHwp2qL.jpg&h=19903455&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86520e86920a2ffac16def1adf62c7998d451d4b","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e88a02a724a53102e3e22196df3e199c7c90776","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"黃店同文宣等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea12d24aa5a3209e15b9be1a64f5984a176e42bc","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df65be1bef163a6dab88d37f9a1fad63a23cd8cc","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e740e26b37d3697b6a165ef0e70204f6a14f608","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef660ba7de0b6cb2030da1cf616073538003e8c9","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f6ab62d0545bc8e05bfed2c5ba8b40ee66da52","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1466b541e25d4a6212da094304720c8d9b36d28","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab51604fc9d185833f0847e77928ceb0e3a3a7b","tid":1907561,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-